a-image-title="houshou_marine_surpassed_kizuna_ai_youtube_subscribers_for_the_first_time_in_japanese_vtuber_history" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/houshou_marine_surpassed_kizuna_ai_youtube_subscribers_for_the_first_time_in_japanese_vtuber_history.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/houshou_marine_surpassed_kizuna_ai_youtube_subscribers_for_the_first_time_in_japanese_vtuber_history.png?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/houshou_marine_surpassed_kizuna_ai_youtube_subscribers_for_the_first_time_in_japanese_vtuber_history.png?resize=1100%2C619&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-111574" data-recalc-dims="1"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：YouTube<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>第一个超过 Kizuna AI 频道订阅人数的达人是 2021 年 7 月 1 日（令和 3）的 Gauru Gura（hololive 英语（hololive-EN）），但<span style="text-decoration: underline;">来自日本的达人是第一次超过这个</span>。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>人才名称</strong></td><td><strong>联系</strong></td><td><strong>订户数量</strong></td></tr><tr><td>高鲁・古拉<br>（高尔·古拉）</td><td>浩乐直播英语</td><td>442万人</td></tr><tr><td>宝生海洋</td><td>霍洛直播</td><td>301万人</td></tr><tr><td>绊爱</td><td>绊爱株式会社</td><td>300万人</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">截至2024年1月10日22:58 </figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ABLVV87_J8-hj34GbjrvGD607HwCCakyj1di1SWxZT9E8rtdw-s5IW51dDok6m5UyB-REEu2bcandfvphMIroplrdklUfQfOguKziyf48PDXW70kpSN6bDf2u1cwjpnCXFlus0EyOAID8cde_VvDrCwZ88dG=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> AIChannel（截至 2024 年 1 月 10 日）<br> © Kizuna AI Inc. </figcaption></figure><p></p><div class="xedar65a0f0ba2c691" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/